sequenceDiagram
    participant PM as "Project Manager"
    participant REQ as "requirements.md<br/>(Phase 5)"
    participant RESEARCH as "research/*.md<br/>(Phase 6)"
    participant SOW as "sow.md<br/>(Phase 8.1)"
    participant EVAL as "evaluate (framework)<br/>(Phase 8.2)"
    participant MARKET as "G-Cloud / DOS<br/>(Phase 8.3)"
    participant VENDOR as "Vendor Proposals"
    participant COMPARE as "evaluate (compare)<br/>(Phase 8.4)"
    participant HLD as "hld-review.md<br/>(Phase 9)"
    
    PM->>REQ: Define requirements (BR/FR/NFR)
    PM->>RESEARCH: Research technology options
    REQ->>SOW: Generate RFP/ITT
    
    SOW->>EVAL: Create evaluation framework
    EVAL->>EVAL: Define criteria & weights
    EVAL->>MARKET: Publish to Digital Marketplace (UK Gov)
    
    MARKET->>VENDOR: Receive vendor proposals
    VENDOR->>COMPARE: Score proposals against framework
    COMPARE->>COMPARE: Generate comparison & recommendation
    
    COMPARE->>PM: Procurement decision
    PM->>HLD: Winning vendor submits HLD
